        {
          "_key": "58516436fdd3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "I was fortunate to have written a book about Sony ACID Pro, "
        },
        {
          "_key": "8074f4a0ae3a",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "aa41e84daf77"
          ],
          "text": "Instant ACID"
        },
        {
          "_key": "cb530937fa33",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": " , which is both an introductory and in-depth tutorial written by myself and Iaccobus gets you started quickly and then dives into the tips and techniques that I use to get the most out of ACID Pro."
        }
