        {
          "_key": "88f045cfe32c",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": " completes the circle of Instant books for the core Sony Media Software products alongside Instant Vegas and Instant Sound Forge. Iacobus, My co-author, and I were beta testers for ACID Pro 5.0 and regular contributors to online forums in the ACID communities. You can read a review of the book on "
        },
